snippet.title: Technobabylon character teaser: Max Lao
snippet.description:
Available on Steam and GOG, coming to iPhone/iPad on August 16, 2017

Other character teasers:
Charlie Regis: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w6Z5-KHbKXQ
Latha Sesame: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x8fkRKoNdso

Max Lao from the upcoming Technobabylon: a cyberpunk adventure game coming this spring from Wadjet Eye Games!
http://www.technobabylon-game.com

Max Lao a tech-savvy case officer who’s very much a product of her society, finds herself torn between two loyalties. When she’s asked to apprehend her best friend and partner, she must choose to follow her feelings or the law.

Technobabylon developed by: Technocrat Games
Published by: Wadjet Eye Games
Max Lao voiced by: Arielle Siegel (http://www.ariellesiegel.com/)
Art by: Ben Chandler
Music by: Premium Beats

Follow the development on Twitter with @wadjeteyegames and @technocratgames!

http://www.wadjeteyegames.com
http://www.technocratgames.com
